The format of a simple reflex based agent without any internal model of the world

function SIMPLE_RELFEX_AGENT(percept) returns an action
persistent: rules, a set of condition-action rules
state <-- INTERPRET-INPUT(percept)
rule <-- RULE_MATCH(state,rules)   //A function that matches a matches the state of the board to the rules of the unit      (THIS IS ESSENTIALLY THE CONDITIONAL NEST ALGORITHM)
action <-- rule.Action
return action

